dashboard_item_ids.name: Product Sales Comparison
dashboard_item_ids.query:
SELECT
    pt. id AS product_id,
    pt.name AS product_name,
    pt.categ_id AS category_id,
    pc.name AS category_name, 
    SUM(sol.price_subtotal) AS total_sales
FROM
    product_template pt
JOIN
    sale_order_line sol ON pt.id = sol.product_id
JOIN
    product_category pc ON pt.categ_id = pc.id
GROUP BY
    pt.id, pt. name, pt.categ_id, pc. name
ORDER BY
    total_sales DESC

dashboard_item_ids.name: Opportunity Pipelines
dashboard_item_ids.query:
SELECT
    s.name AS stage_name,
    COUNT(l.id) AS opportunities_count
FROM
    crm_lead l
JOIN
    crm_stage s ON l.stage_id = s.id
WHERE
    l.active = 'true'  -- Consider only active opportunities
GROUP BY
    s.name, s.sequence
ORDER BY
    s.sequence
